{"tid":2241562,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是飽晚","createTime":"2020-10-13T11:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T13:43:58.000Z","uid":268868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38546ac21faf3432a4523971d9ec6293479e7462","tid":2241562,"uid":268868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"好耐無整野食<br />\n又好耐無食餃子<br />\n決定就用屋企有既野包餃子 <br />\n<br />\n由餃子皮開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVsw2Xd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVsw2Xd.jpg&h=4ad4e3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己搓既皮係好食啲 <br />\n餡係冬菇西芹雞肉 <br />\n（無計 屋企有乜落乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n包完出嚟勁大隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zunpDwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzunpDwP.jpg&h=a3c90574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身隻餃勁大隻<br />\n自己搓既皮烚完又厚過買返嚟嗰啲<br />\n食咗6隻已經飽咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOw57q4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOw57q4.jpg&h=5fe07d35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"638a36838bf0b2fec02a298ca26de34687b3902a","tid":2241562,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"巨餃師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73f79a08cbc1d6e1149430b18b56f0dad5ced93","tid":2241562,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"韓國王餃子都好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5aa55fec3cece16964d209622d4f5aa81d6bd7","tid":2241562,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset